{"tid":37242,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"橋本環奈專屬「處刑技」，同台女藝人超痛苦","createTime":"2016-12-13T08:42:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T18:58:06.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb338d8e905cb7da63741ee7362486e76704fc1c","tid":37242,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"有著「千年一遇」美稱的橋本環奈除了有「天使光環」回血技，還有專屬「處刑技」，可單放也可打範圍，人多時效過更佳。使用時機：和別的藝人一起出席活動時，只要天使一站出來放出「處刑技」，有哪位女藝人膽敢站在她旁邊，保證1秒被比下去，處刑無誤。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼差很多對吧？<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153651.jpg&h=f3d3f9f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼就算穿制服三打一，也難敵環奈魅力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153648.jpg&h=fbe7f69e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼Berryz工房雖然很紅，但如果出來單挑，結果好像有點...<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153649.jpg&h=374df600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼就桐谷美玲也不是對手！看她臉這麼臭XD<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153656.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153656.jpg&h=f916f0ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼松井玲奈也被擊沉，但以上都還不是最慘...<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153647.jpg&h=22c7e432&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▼小島瑠璃子真是太太太慘啦！不過可能是派大星想太多，瑠璃子看起來感覺還蠻開心的XD。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/1153/1153650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F1153%2F1153650.jpg&h=3f79f968&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網友表示：<br />\n<br />\n「AKB48本來就不是每個都很正！」<br />\n「橋本環奈太強了啦！」<br />\n「這樣比不公平啦。」<br />\n「完全同意，橋本環奈真的很正。」<br />\n「公開處刑無誤。」<br />\n<br />\n派大星覺得橋本環奈真的很強，從第一張「千年一遇」寫真到現在，居然都沒有長壞，還是這麼正，能贏過她的我看只有16歲時的渡邊麻友了..."},{"pid":"46f88296df5ebe29535ee19747504b1e0133b7f9","tid":37242,"uid":22694,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:42:56.000Z","msg":"山本彩正囉屌"},{"pid":"75d6247ebf5dc3698ab2f13ebf61fe9d1db7756d","tid":37242,"uid":5077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:44:06.000Z","msg":"16歲時的渡邊麻友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6894f81a1084a85e3ea8517aa6c23d44aa3b9881","tid":37242,"uid":46231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山本彩正囉屌</blockquote><br />\n山本彩正囉屌"},{"pid":"ea3cf2a1f549bda43a3bc59158874860d9081635","tid":37242,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:44:07.000Z","msg":"miruru完勝"},{"pid":"d2d692ca534a9486623bf75aa2acb3f3191f4e7c","tid":37242,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:44:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>山本彩正囉屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n彩姐正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f540b74fb8becee737c57fd9e10e65feb110c52","tid":37242,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:44:54.000Z","msg":"wow"},{"pid":"187376c748e2965130f40b2170447642decb37cd","tid":37242,"uid":33428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:46:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>山本彩正囉屌</blockquote><br />\n山本彩正囉屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n山本彩正囉屌"},{"pid":"608556dfb61327b5d62da454dcdcf1732ffa0845","tid":37242,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"梁烈惟"},{"pid":"5c5ca34d228be0f02718765b29b71bc564dd7db3","tid":37242,"uid":660,"like"